pubspec.name: web_socket_channel
pubspec.author: Dart Team <misc@dartlang.org>
pubspec.description: StreamChannel wrappers for WebSockets. This package provides a cross-platform WebSocketChannel API, a cross-platform implementation of that API that communicates over an underlying StreamChannel, IOWebSocketChannel that wraps dart:io's WebSocket class, and a HtmlWebSocketChannel that wrap's dart:html's.
